Hi,
The piece of code below gives a richer information
at /proc/PID/status for a process PID.
BR,
Edjard
-------------------------------------------------------------------
10LE - Linux Lab at INDT
JOSE - Open Source dEvelopers at ufam.edu.br (site still under construction)
